response.overview: The Angels are charged with finding a pair of missing rings that are encoded with the personal information of members of the Witness Protection Program. As informants are killed, the ladies target a rogue agent who might be responsible.
response.tagline: This summer the Angels are back.
response.title: Charlie's Angels: Full Throttle
